### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "u1",
  "lineItems": [
    { "productId": "60f1b0b3b3f1b3f1b3f1b3f1", "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "paymentMode": "CARD",
  "shippingAddress": {
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "house": "221B",
    "street": "Baker Street",
    "city": "London",
    "zip": "NW16XE"
  }
}

### Stream all orders (SSE)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Accept: text/event-stream

### Get all orders (plain JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Accept: application/json
